<td>Content-heavy SEO teams</td>
<td>Less suited for deadline management</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table></div>
<p>Start with Google Sheets if you are managing fewer than 5 clients. Move to a dedicated project management tool when you hit 10+ active campaigns and manual updates become the bottleneck. The sections in this guide work in any format.</p>
